WEBVTT

00:05:57.600 --> 00:06:01.096
if even engaged workaholics
need to disconnect from work.

00:06:01.120 --> 00:06:02.376
You can overdo it.

00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.736
And it will catch up to you eventually.

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:06.136
After her wake-up call,

00:06:06.160 --> 00:06:09.960
Arianna decided she desperately
needed more boundaries and more sleep.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:13.176
AH: I get eight hours
95 percent of the time

00:06:13.200 --> 00:06:18.040
because that's my optimal time
for me to wake up fully recharged.

00:06:19.720 --> 00:06:23.136
I prioritize little tiny
breaks during the day

00:06:23.160 --> 00:06:28.976
and I'm very absolute about my end-of-day
and beginning-of-day rituals.

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:30.616
Turning off my phone,